I0702 18:36:43.296356    2153 conn_opt.go:55] jsonrpc2: --> request #47: conversation/chat/updateHistory: {"History":[{"entity":"USER","markdownText":"quiero crear una pagina para vender PPF (Paint Protection Film) expecificamente de la marca Gyeon, la idea es traccionar clientes desde la pagina a talleres certificados por la marca, la pagina solo debe tener expecificacioes sobre el ppf, mantenimiento, y talleres ","chatSectionId":"0","ideContext":{"currentFile":{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/README-cloudshell.txt","language":"plaintext","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"CURRENTLY_OPEN","isUntitled":false},"remoteContexts":null,"remoteRepositories":[],"otherFiles":[{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request.yml","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/mcp/dist/index.js","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/skills/bigquery/references/graph/graph-schema/feature_parity.md","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/config.yml","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/question.yml","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/bug_report.yml","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.config/powershell/Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/shebang-command/package.json","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/shebang-regex/package.json","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false}],"rules":null,"editableRegion":null,"recentUserActions":null,"chatSectionId":"0"},"id":"dcd5591b-cd96-4a06-b81d-02a2265d0314","agentMetadata":{"coderAgent":{"kind":""},"model":""}},{"traceId":"1c53a5d2cf59436e","entity":"SYSTEM","markdownText":"¡Excelente iniciativa! Crear una página enfocada en la conversión hacia talleres certificados es una gran estrategia para posicionar la marca **Gyeon** y asegurar un servicio de calidad.\n\nPara una página de este tipo, lo ideal es un diseño limpio, profesional y con mucha carga visual (fotos de autos con acabado brillante). Aquí tienes una propuesta de estructura y código utilizando **Tailwind CSS** (vía CDN para facilitar las pruebas) que cubre exactamente lo que necesitas: Especificaciones, Mantenimiento y Talleres.\n\n### Sugerencia de Estructura:\n1.  **Hero Section:** Una imagen impactante de un coche protegido con Gyeon PPF y un llamado a la acción (CTA).\n2.  **Especificaciones:** Resaltar la tecnología de Gyeon (autocuración, hidrofobia, brillo).\n3.  **Mantenimiento:** Una guía rápida de cómo cuidar el film para extender su garantía.\n4.  **Red de Talleres:** Un buscador o lista de centros certificados.\n\nAquí tienes el código base para comenzar:\n\n```diff\n--- /dev/null\n+++ /home/obsidian_detailers/index.html\n@@ -0,0 +1,155 @@\n+\u003c!DOCTYPE html\u003e\n+\u003chtml lang=\"es\"\u003e\n+\u003chead\u003e\n+    \u003cmeta charset=\"UTF-8\"\u003e\n+    \u003cmeta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"\u003e\n+    \u003ctitle\u003eGyeon PPF - Protección Invisible de Clase Mundial\u003c/title\u003e\n+    \u003cscript src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"\u003e\u003c/script\u003e\n+    \u003clink href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;700\u0026display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"\u003e\n+    \u003cstyle\u003e\n+        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }\n+        .gradient-overlay { background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 100%); }\n+    \u003c/style\u003e\n+\u003c/head\u003e\n+\u003cbody class=\"bg-gray-50 text-gray-900\"\u003e\n+\n+    \u003c!-- Hero Section --\u003e\n+    \u003cheader class=\"relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center text-white overflow-hidden\"\u003e\n+        \u003cimg src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?auto=format\u0026fit=crop\u0026q=80\u0026w=2000\" alt=\"Gyeon PPF Car\" class=\"absolute w-full h-full object-cover\"\u003e\n+        \u003cdiv class=\"absolute w-full h-full gradient-overlay\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n+        \u003cdiv class=\"relative z-10 text-center px-4\"\u003e\n+            \u003ch1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tighter\"\u003eGYEON PPF\u003c/h1\u003e\n+            \u003cp class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-300\"\u003eLa máxima protección contra impactos y agentes externos con tecnología de autocuración avanzada.\u003c/p\u003e\n+            \u003ca href=\"#talleres\" class=\"bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold transition-all transform hover:scale-105\"\u003eEncontrar Taller Certificado\u003c/a\u003e\n+        \u003c/div\u003e\n+    \u003c/header\u003e\n+\n+    \u003c!-- Especificaciones --\u003e\n+    \u003csection id=\"especificaciones\" class=\"py-20 bg-white\"\u003e\n+        \u003cdiv class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6\"\u003e\n+            \u003ch2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-16 underline decoration-blue-600 underline-offset-8\"\u003eEspecificaciones Técnicas\u003c/h2\u003e\n+            \u003cdiv class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12\"\u003e\n+                \u003cdiv class=\"text-center\"\u003e\n+                    \u003cdiv class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold\"\u003e01\u003c/div\u003e\n+                    \u003ch3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\"\u003eAutocuración\u003c/h3\u003e\n+                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\"\u003eLos rayones leves y marcas de remolino desaparecen con la exposición al calor o agua caliente.\u003c/p\u003e\n+                \u003c/div\u003e\n+                \u003cdiv class=\"text-center\"\u003e\n+                    \u003cdiv class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold\"\u003e02\u003c/div\u003e\n+                    \u003ch3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\"\u003eSúper Hidrofóbico\u003c/h3\u003e\n+                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\"\u003eRepele agua y suciedad de forma extrema, facilitando la limpieza y manteniendo el auto impecable por más tiempo.\u003c/p\u003e\n+                \u003c/div\u003e\n+                \u003cdiv class=\"text-center\"\u003e\n+                    \u003cdiv class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold\"\u003e03\u003c/div\u003e\n+                    \u003ch3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\"\u003eResistencia UV\u003c/h3\u003e\n+                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\"\u003eProtección total contra el amarilleo y la degradación causada por los rayos solares.\u003c/p\u003e\n+                \u003c/div\u003e\n+            \u003c/div\u003e\n+        \u003c/div\u003e\n+    \u003c/section\u003e\n+\n+    \u003c!-- Mantenimiento --\u003e\n+    \u003csection id=\"mantenimiento\" class=\"py-20 bg-gray-900 text-white\"\u003e\n+        \u003cdiv class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6\"\u003e\n+            \u003cdiv class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12\"\u003e\n+                \u003cdiv class=\"md:w-1/2\"\u003e\n+                    \u003ch2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\"\u003eGuía de Mantenimiento\u003c/h2\u003e\n+                    \u003cul class=\"space-y-4\"\u003e\n+                        \u003cli class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n+                            \u003cspan class=\"text-blue-500 mr-2\"\u003e✔\u003c/span\u003e\n+                            \u003cspan\u003eLavar con shampoo PH Neutro (Gyeon Q²M PPF Wash).\u003c/span\u003e\n+                        \u003c/li\u003e\n+                        \u003cli class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n+                            \u003cspan class=\"text-blue-500 mr-2\"\u003e✔\u003c/span\u003e\n+                            \u003cspan\u003eNo lavar el vehículo bajo el sol directo o con la superficie caliente.\u003c/span\u003e\n+                        \u003c/li\u003e\n+                        \u003cli class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n+                            \u003cspan class=\"text-blue-500 mr-2\"\u003e✔\u003c/span\u003e\n+                            \u003cspan\u003eUsar selladores específicos como Gyeon Q²M PPF Maintain.\u003c/span\u003e\n+                        \u003c/li\u003e\n+                        \u003cli class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n+                            \u003cspan class=\"text-red-500 mr-2\"\u003e✘\u003c/span\u003e\n+                            \u003cspan class=\"text-gray-400\"\u003eEvitar el uso de hidrolavadoras a menos de 50cm de los bordes.\u003c/span\u003e\n+                        \u003c/li\u003e\n+                    \u003c/ul\u003e\n+                \u003c/div\u003e\n+                \u003cdiv class=\"md:w-1/2 bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700\"\u003e\n+                    \u003cp class=\"italic text-gray-400\"\u003e\"El mantenimiento adecuado garantiza que la garantía de fábrica se mantenga vigente y que el brillo se conserve por años.\"\u003c/p\u003e\n+                \u003c/div\u003e\n+            \u003c/div\u003e\n+        \u003c/div\u003e\n+    \u003c/section\u003e\n+\n+    \u003c!-- Talleres Certificados --\u003e\n+    \u003csection id=\"talleres\" class=\"py-20 bg-white\"\u003e\n+        \u003cdiv class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6\"\u003e\n+            \u003ch2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4\"\u003eTalleres Certificados GYEON\u003c/h2\u003e\n+            \u003cp class=\"text-center text-gray-500 mb-12\"\u003eSolo los centros certificados garantizan la correcta instalación y garantía oficial.\u003c/p\u003e\n+            \n+            \u003cdiv class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left\"\u003e\n+                \u003c!-- Taller Card --\u003e\n+                \u003cdiv class=\"border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow\"\u003e\n+                    \u003ch4 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-2\"\u003eDetailing Center Norte\u003c/h4\u003e\n+                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4\"\u003eCalle Principal 123, Ciudad de México\u003c/p\u003e\n+                    \u003ca href=\"https://wa.me/123456789\" class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline\"\u003eContactar por WhatsApp →\u003c/a\u003e\n+                \u003c/div\u003e\n+                \n+                \u003cdiv class=\"border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow\"\u003e\n+                    \u003ch4 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-2\"\u003ePremium Shield Studio\u003c/h4\u003e\n+                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4\"\u003eAv. Insurgentes Sur 456, CDMX\u003c/p\u003e\n+                    \u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline\"\u003eVer Ubicación →\u003c/a\u003e\n+                \u003c/div\u003e\n+\n+                \u003cdiv class=\"border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow\"\u003e\n+                    \u003ch4 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-2\"\u003eGyeon Certified Madrid\u003c/h4\u003e\n+                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4\"\u003ePolígono Industrial Oeste, Nave 4\u003c/p\u003e\n+                    \u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline\"\u003eContactar ahora →\u003c/a\u003e\n+                \u003c/div\u003e\n+            \u003c/div\u003e\n+        \u003c/div\u003e\n+    \u003c/section\u003e\n+\n+    \u003cfooter class=\"py-10 bg-gray-50 border-t text-center\"\u003e\n+        \u003cp class=\"text-gray-400 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase\"\u003eGyeon PPF Official Partner\u003c/p\u003e\n+    \u003c/footer\u003e\n+\n+\u003c/body\u003e\n+\u003c/html\u003e\n```\n\n### Por qué esta solución:\n*   **Minimalismo:** Cumple estrictamente con tus tres requisitos (Especificaciones, Mantenimiento, Talleres).\n*   **Filtro de Calidad:** Al enfatizar en la \"Certificación\", educas al cliente de que no debe ir a cualquier lugar, lo que protege el valor de la marca.\n*   **Responsive:** Se ve bien tanto en computadoras como en celulares (donde la mayoría de los clientes buscarán).\n\n**Pasos siguientes recomendados:**\n1.  **Imágenes:** Reemplaza las URLs de las fotos por imágenes reales de trabajos realizados con Gyeon.\n2.  **Formulario:** Si quieres captar datos antes de enviarlos al taller, podrías añadir un pequeño formulario de contacto que pregunte el modelo del auto.\n\n\u003c!--\n[PROMPT_SUGGESTION]¿Cómo puedo agregar un mapa de Google Maps para mostrar la ubicación de los talleres?[/PROMPT_SUGGESTION]\n[PROMPT_SUGGESTION]Añade un formulario de contacto para que el usuario pida presupuesto enviando su modelo de coche[/PROMPT_SUGGESTION]\n--\u003e","chatSectionId":"0","ideContext":{"currentFile":{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/README-cloudshell.txt","language":"plaintext","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"CURRENTLY_OPEN","isUntitled":false},"remoteContexts":null,"remoteRepositories":[],"otherFiles":[{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request.yml","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/mcp/dist/index.js","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/skills/bigquery/references/graph/graph-schema/feature_parity.md","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/config.yml","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/question.yml","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/bug_report.yml","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.config/powershell/Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/shebang-command/package.json","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false},{"path":"/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/shebang-regex/package.json","language":"","selection":{"start":0,"end":0},"includedReason":"RELATED_FILE","isUntitled":false}],"rules":null,"editableRegion":null,"recentUserActions":null,"chatSectionId":"0"},"openFileUri":"file:///home/obsidian_detailers/README-cloudshell.txt","ragStatus":"RAG_NOT_FOUND","timeToFirstToken":"9605","agentProcessingDetails":{},"workspaceChange":{"files":[{"filePath":"/home/obsidian_detailers/index.html","newText":"\u003c!DOCTYPE html\u003e\n\u003chtml lang=\"es\"\u003e\n\u003chead\u003e\n    \u003cmeta charset=\"UTF-8\"\u003e\n    \u003cmeta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"\u003e\n    \u003ctitle\u003eGyeon PPF - Protección Invisible de Clase Mundial\u003c/title\u003e\n    \u003cscript src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"\u003e\u003c/script\u003e\n    \u003clink href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;700\u0026display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"\u003e\n    \u003cstyle\u003e\n        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }\n        .gradient-overlay { background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 100%); }\n    \u003c/style\u003e\n\u003c/head\u003e\n\u003cbody class=\"bg-gray-50 text-gray-900\"\u003e\n\n    \u003c!-- Hero Section --\u003e\n    \u003cheader class=\"relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center text-white overflow-hidden\"\u003e\n        \u003cimg src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?auto=format\u0026fit=crop\u0026q=80\u0026w=2000\" alt=\"Gyeon PPF Car\" class=\"absolute w-full h-full object-cover\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"absolute w-full h-full gradient-overlay\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"relative z-10 text-center px-4\"\u003e\n            \u003ch1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tighter\"\u003eGYEON PPF\u003c/h1\u003e\n            \u003cp class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-300\"\u003eLa máxima protección contra impactos y agentes externos con tecnología de autocuración avanzada.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003ca href=\"#talleres\" class=\"bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold transition-all transform hover:scale-105\"\u003eEncontrar Taller Certificado\u003c/a\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/header\u003e\n\n    \u003c!-- Especificaciones --\u003e\n    \u003csection id=\"especificaciones\" class=\"py-20 bg-white\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6\"\u003e\n            \u003ch2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-16 underline decoration-blue-600 underline-offset-8\"\u003eEspecificaciones Técnicas\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12\"\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"text-center\"\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold\"\u003e01\u003c/div\u003e\n                    \u003ch3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\"\u003eAutocuración\u003c/h3\u003e\n                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\"\u003eLos rayones leves y marcas de remolino desaparecen con la exposición al calor o agua caliente.\u003c/p\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"text-center\"\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold\"\u003e02\u003c/div\u003e\n                    \u003ch3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\"\u003eSúper Hidrofóbico\u003c/h3\u003e\n                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\"\u003eRepele agua y suciedad de forma extrema, facilitando la limpieza y manteniendo el auto impecable por más tiempo.\u003c/p\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"text-center\"\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold\"\u003e03\u003c/div\u003e\n                    \u003ch3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\"\u003eResistencia UV\u003c/h3\u003e\n                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\"\u003eProtección total contra el amarilleo y la degradación causada por los rayos solares.\u003c/p\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/section\u003e\n\n    \u003c!-- Mantenimiento --\u003e\n    \u003csection id=\"mantenimiento\" class=\"py-20 bg-gray-900 text-white\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12\"\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"md:w-1/2\"\u003e\n                    \u003ch2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\"\u003eGuía de Mantenimiento\u003c/h2\u003e\n                    \u003cul class=\"space-y-4\"\u003e\n                        \u003cli class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n                            \u003cspan class=\"text-blue-500 mr-2\"\u003e✔\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003cspan\u003eLavar con shampoo PH Neutro (Gyeon Q²M PPF Wash).\u003c/span\u003e\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                        \u003cli class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n                            \u003cspan class=\"text-blue-500 mr-2\"\u003e✔\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003cspan\u003eNo lavar el vehículo bajo el sol directo o con la superficie caliente.\u003c/span\u003e\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                        \u003cli class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n                            \u003cspan class=\"text-blue-500 mr-2\"\u003e✔\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003cspan\u003eUsar selladores específicos como Gyeon Q²M PPF Maintain.\u003c/span\u003e\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                        \u003cli class=\"flex items-start\"\u003e\n                            \u003cspan class=\"text-red-500 mr-2\"\u003e✘\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003cspan class=\"text-gray-400\"\u003eEvitar el uso de hidrolavadoras a menos de 50cm de los bordes.\u003c/span\u003e\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003c/ul\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"md:w-1/2 bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700\"\u003e\n                    \u003cp class=\"italic text-gray-400\"\u003e\"El mantenimiento adecuado garantiza que la garantía de fábrica se mantenga vigente y que el brillo se conserve por años.\"\u003c/p\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/section\u003e\n\n    \u003c!-- Talleres Certificados --\u003e\n    \u003csection id=\"talleres\" class=\"py-20 bg-white\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6\"\u003e\n            \u003ch2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4\"\u003eTalleres Certificados GYEON\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003cp class=\"text-center text-gray-500 mb-12\"\u003eSolo los centros certificados garantizan la correcta instalación y garantía oficial.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \n            \u003cdiv class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left\"\u003e\n                \u003c!-- Taller Card --\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow\"\u003e\n                    \u003ch4 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-2\"\u003eDetailing Center Norte\u003c/h4\u003e\n                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4\"\u003eCalle Principal 123, Ciudad de México\u003c/p\u003e\n                    \u003ca href=\"https://wa.me/123456789\" class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline\"\u003eContactar por WhatsApp →\u003c/a\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n                \u003cdiv class=\"border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow\"\u003e\n                    \u003ch4 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-2\"\u003ePremium Shield Studio\u003c/h4\u003e\n                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4\"\u003eAv. Insurgentes Sur 456, CDMX\u003c/p\u003e\n                    \u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline\"\u003eVer Ubicación →\u003c/a\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                \u003cdiv class=\"border rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow\"\u003e\n                    \u003ch4 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-2\"\u003eGyeon Certified Madrid\u003c/h4\u003e\n                    \u003cp class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4\"\u003ePolígono Industrial Oeste, Nave 4\u003c/p\u003e\n                    \u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline\"\u003eContactar ahora →\u003c/a\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/section\u003e\n\n    \u003cfooter class=\"py-10 bg-gray-50 border-t text-center\"\u003e\n        \u003cp class=\"text-gray-400 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase\"\u003eGyeon PPF Official Partner\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/footer\u003e\n\n\u003c/body\u003e\n\u003c/html\u003e","telemetry":{"CommentLines":null},"codeBlockIndex":0,"language":"html","checkpointFileNotFound":true,"accepted":true}]},"fileUsage":{"includedFiles":["/home/obsidian_detailers/README-cloudshell.txt","/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request.yml","/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/mcp/dist/index.js","/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pack/skills/bigquery/references/graph/graph-schema/feature_parity.md","/home/obsidian_detailers/.npm/_npx/2fc3aa65c5ea3212/node_modules/data-agent-kit-starter-pac